Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,星舰即将到达鯨魚座ο3号行星，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Approaching Omicron Ceti III, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,调整轨道，裴恩特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Standard orbit, Mr. Painter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.49,0:00:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰长？ - 怎么了，上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Captain? - Yes, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我遵照指示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been transmitting a contact signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,每5分钟发送一次通讯信号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}every five minutes as ordered, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可是完全没有回应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All I get is dead air. Shall I continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,继续发送信号，直到我们进入轨道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maintain transmission pattern until we've established orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 遵命，长官 - 史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Aye, aye, sir. - Mr. Spock,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.13,0:00:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那颗星球上有150名男女和儿童\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}there were 150 men, women and children in that colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.76,0:00:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为他们生还的概率是多少？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are the chances of survivors?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.59,0:00:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不可能还活着，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Absolutely none, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.09,0:00:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,博托射线是最近才被发现的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Berthold rays are such a recent discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还不完全了解它的性质\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We do not yet have full knowledge of their nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但有一点是确定的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is known, however, that living animal tissue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这种射线会分解动物组织\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}disintegrates under exposure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.85,0:00:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,桑多瓦尔和他的部下们不可能挺过三年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sandoval's group could not have survived after three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说他们早知如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're saying that those people
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.11,0:01:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,却仍试着在那开荒？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}built a future in a place knowing they might not survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.40,0:01:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,也许他们认为射线并不那么致命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm saying they knew there was a risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.49,0:01:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我们呢，能不能登陆？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about us? Can we afford to send people down to the planet surface?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.78,0:01:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,射线的破坏作用需要一个过程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The breakdown of tissue does not develop immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.62,0:01:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能耐受一定程度的辐射\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can risk a limited exposure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.79,0:01:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,星舰进入轨道，舰长，殖民地已定位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've established orbit, sir. And I've pinpointed a settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.38,0:01:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，裴恩特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you, Mr. Painter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.84,0:01:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,组织一个五人登陆小队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Equip a landing party of five to accompany me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.17,0:01:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,跟随我前往星球表面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to the planet surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,安排麦考伊和一名生物学家与我们同行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Include Dr. McCoy and a biologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们在10分钟之内准备好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll want them in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,又是一次失败的殖民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Another dream that failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.35,0:02:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没有比这更让人伤感的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's nothing sadder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.35,0:02:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人花了一年的时间从地球出发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It took these people a year to make the trip from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,长途跋涉来到这里……\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They came all that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,……然后死去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.36,0:02:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是呢，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hardly that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.78,0:02:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到鯨魚座ο3号行星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Welcome to Omicron Ceti III.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我是伊莱亚斯·桑多瓦尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm Elias Sandoval.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙，最后的边疆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Space, the final frontier.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这是星舰进取号的航程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These are the voyages Of the starship Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:03:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,它的五年任务，是去探索未知的新世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Its five-year mission: To explore strange new worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,找寻新的生命和新的文明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to seek out new life and new civilizations,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢地航向前人未至之境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to boldly go where no man has gone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,【星际迷航：原初】
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}TLF荣誉出品\N本字幕仅供学习交流，严禁用于商业途径{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H00FFFF&}-=TLF字幕组=-\N翻译：Nick\N校对：喜马拉雅{\c}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,第一季第二十四集\N人间天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历3417.3\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 3417.3.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.44,0:03:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们本以为此次鯨魚座ο3号之旅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We thought our mission to Omicron Ceti III
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,将会充满悲伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}would be an unhappy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们早已断定这个殖民地再无生还者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We had expected to find no survivors of the agricultural colony there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.03,0:03:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但显然，我们错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Apparently, our information was incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们离开地球已有四年了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We haven't seen anyone outside our own group for four years
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.91,0:04:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这期间从未遇到过其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}since we left the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直在等候你们这些客人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've been expecting someone for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的子空间无线电设备无法正常运作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our subspace radio didn't work properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,而且这里也没有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm afraid we didn't have anyone here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,会修理这复杂的设备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who could master its intricacies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,桑多瓦尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Actually, Mr. Sandoval,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们并不是因为你们的设备故障而来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we didn't come here because of your silent radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你们为何而来，我们都欢迎你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It makes little difference, captain. You're here. We're happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,来，我带你们参观一下定居点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come, let me show you our settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,根据我的观察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On pure speculation, just an educated guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个活人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd say that man is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我们的情报表明\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, this planet is being bombarded by Berthold rays,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这颗行星正受到博托射线的照射\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as our reports indicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.65,0:04:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能在这种强度的辐射中安全地存活一周\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}At this intensity, we'll be safe for a week, if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,但是……\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这些人不应该还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But these people shouldn't be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,难道他们已经死了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is it possible that they're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是握手了吗，吉姆？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You shook hands with him, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,他的手是暖的，他还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His flesh was warm. He's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.09,0:04:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这毫无疑问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no doubt about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但博托射线是致命的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is also no question on the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这也同样毫无疑问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that Berthold rays are incontrovertibly deadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你要知道，麦考伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no miracle connected with it, doctor. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.43,0:04:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,足够剂量的辐射会杀死人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No cures, no serums, no antidotes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,无法治疗，没有血清和解药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If a man is exposed long enough, he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,各位，多说无益\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gentlemen, we're debating in a vacuum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,还是一起去寻找答案吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's go get some answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有另外两处村落，而这里有45名居民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are two other settlements, but we have 45 colonists here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要分散开来？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What was the reason for the dispersal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,分成三处的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, we felt that three groups
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,繁衍壮大的可能性更高\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}would have a better chance for growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果疾病侵袭了其中一个村落\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If disease were to strike one group,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.13,0:05:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,另外两处不易受到影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}then the others would be less likely to be affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,ο星非常适合农业开发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see, Omicron is an ideal agricultural planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们之前，失败的先例有很多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We determined not to suffer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们绝不希望重蹈覆辙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the fate of expeditions that went before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,伊莱亚斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,利拉，来见见我们的客人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Leila, come meet our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的植物学家利拉·卡罗米\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Leila Kalomi, our botanist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这是寇克舰长，麦考伊医生，史波克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Captain Kirk, Dr. McCoy, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生和我曾有过一面之缘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock and I have met before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,在很久以前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,桑多瓦尔先生，我们来这里是有任务的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Sandoval, we do have a mission here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 需要进行一系列检查，测试 - 没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Examinations. Tests. - By all means, make them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你们会对这里感兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think you'll find our settlement an interesting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有一个很简单的理想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our philosophy is a simple one:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是让人类回归简单的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That men should return to a less-complicated life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这里机器很少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have few mechanical things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没有车辆，也没有武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No vehicles, no weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这里没有暴力，充满和平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have harmony here. Complete peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会尽量避免干扰你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll try not to interfere with your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,请自便吧，先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Make yourselves at home, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们到底要找什么呢，长官？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What exactly are we looking for anyway, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,任何看起来不正常的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Whatever doesn't look right. Whatever that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不熟悉农场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When it comes to farms,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,只有靠近点看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wouldn't know what looked right or wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,才能发现问题所在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if it were 2 feet from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.16,0:07:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.33,0:07:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没有牛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No cows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这棚子并不用来圈养牲口，而是用来存放东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This barn isn't even built for them, just for storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细想想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们好像没见过任何动物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we haven't seen any animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没有马，没有猪，连狗都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No horses, no pigs. Not even a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.85,0:07:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没有任何牲畜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.64,0:07:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识那个瓦肯星人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've known the Vulcanian.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，六年前在地球上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On Earth. Six years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你爱他吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you love him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我暗恋着他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I did, it was important only to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那么他呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How did he feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他从未流露过他对我的感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock's feelings were never expressed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.57,0:08:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,据说他没有情感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It is said he has none to give.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那你现在希望他留下来，成为我们的一员吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Would you like him to stay with us now? To be as one of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,他会留下来的，伊莱亚斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is no choice, Elias.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He will stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了，谢谢你的配合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That will be all. Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么发现吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经检查了9名男性，年龄从23到59岁不等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've examined nine men so far, varying in ages from 23 to 59.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.24,0:08:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的健康状况都很完美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're all in perfect condition. Textbook responses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,心肺功能极佳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Heart, lungs, excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.32,0:08:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,协调度极佳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Coordination, excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,神经反射正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Reflexes, excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如果所有人都像他们这样，我就可以扔掉行医执照了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If there were many more of them, I could throw away my shingle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我是寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.42,0:08:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我是史波克，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock here, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,除了殖民地居民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There seems to be a total absence of life on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,以及各种植被\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with the exception of the colonists themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.80,0:09:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这颗星球上似乎没有其他生物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and various types of flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这和苏鲁的观察一致\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sulu had the same observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Any explanations?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还不清楚，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not at the moment, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.30,0:09:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在使用三录仪进行各种测试\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm conducting various tests with the tricorder,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但还没得到结论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but results are inconclusive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很好，继续进行调查，寇克呼叫完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very well. Continue investigations. Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没有动物，真是奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No animals. That's peculiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.69,0:09:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，而且根据记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, especially in view of the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们曾经饲养过一些动物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that the records of this expedition indicate that they did have some
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,用于繁殖、食用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for breeding and food purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,显然，它们都没能活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Apparently, none of them survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.87,0:09:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看看他们的医疗记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd like to see the medical records on the expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我想你应该看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I thought you might.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我在找你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没参观过我们的田地和作物吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You haven't seen our fields and crops.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我想带你们去看看我们的成果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'd like to show you and the doctor what we've accomplished here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我恐怕要失陪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm afraid I'll have to bow out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.63,0:09:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我还要继续做一些医学检测\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have to continue with these medical examinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.51,0:09:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我发现其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}However, if I find everyone else's health
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,也和你一样健康的话，我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to be as perfect as yours, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.31,0:09:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他就要扔掉他的行医执照了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He promised to throw away his shingle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我恐怕你是找不到病人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you'll find no weaklings here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:09:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，请\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.02,0:10:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是答案，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the reason, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,所有作物都能在这种土壤中生长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This soil will grow anything we plant in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一个完美的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a perfect world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,气候温和\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have a moderate climate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,全年都有适度的降水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Moderate rains all year round.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,能为我们提供需要的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It gives us all we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就像是伊甸园 - 舰长，打扰一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It is perfect. - Pardon me, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,生物报告出来了，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Biology report ready, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我有事失陪了，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I have work to tend to myself, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.13,0:10:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,说吧，上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go ahead, lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,桑多瓦尔说他们能种植任何作物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I heard Sandoval saying they could grow anything here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,事实的确如此，谷类、马铃薯、豆类\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's true, sir. They've got a variety of crops in. Grains, potatoes, beans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你想说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Make your point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,对于一个农业殖民地来说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, sir, for an agricultural colony,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的耕种面积太小了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}they actually have very little acreage planted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,生产的粮食仅够维持生活，几乎没有剩余\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's enough to sustain the colony, but very little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切实在太奇怪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's like a jigsaw puzzle, all one colour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而我们一点头绪都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No key to where the pieces fit in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我是寇克 - 我是麦考伊，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Kirk here. - This is McCoy, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想你最好回来一下 - 出什么事了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I think you better get back here. - Trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，但我想让你亲眼看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, but I'd like you to see this for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:10:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.42,0:11:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,桑多瓦尔的医疗记录显示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sandoval's medical record
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,4年前，当此次殖民行动开始时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}four years ago, when the expedition left Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.21,0:11:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,仪器检测出了他肺部的疤痕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He registered scar tissue on his lungs
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他小时候患大叶性肺炎时留下的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from lobar pneumonia suffered when he was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,除了切掉阑尾他没动过大手术\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No major operations, but there was an appendectomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,还接受了计划免疫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Received all required inoculations, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.31,0:11:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这有什么奇怪的？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's so strange about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但不到2个小时前我检查过他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I examined that man not more than two hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道结果如何吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you know what his readings were?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都很完美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Perfect, perfect and perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.86,0:11:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就像这里的其他人一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just like everyone else I've examined here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是仪器发生故障了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Instrument malfunction?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没有，我用它来检测自己的情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I thought of that, and I tested it on myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,它准确地记录了我的扁桃体切除史\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It accurately recorded my lack of tonsils
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,还有两处肋骨骨折\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and those two broken ribs I had once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,它没有检测到桑多瓦尔肺部的瘢痕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It did not record the scar tissue on Sandoval's lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但却检测到他体内有一条健康的阑尾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it did record a healthy appendix
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,而那本不应该存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}where one was supposedly removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.05,0:11:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,连虫子都没有一条\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing. Not even insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但作物却在生长，而你们也能在博托射线照射下存活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yet your plants grow, and you've survived exposure to Berthold rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这是可以解释的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That can be explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.69,0:12:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,请告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,再等等吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.15,0:12:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法了解为什么女性\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've never understood the female capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要回避正面回答问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to avoid a direct answer to any question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不了解你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I never understood you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,直到现在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,从未有人能进入你的内心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There was always a place in here where no one could come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是一副扑克脸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There was only the face you allow people to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,别人只能看到你的一面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only one side you'd allow them to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.30,0:12:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I would like to know how your people
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是如何活下来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}have managed to survive here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我好想你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.77,0:12:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,理论上讲，你们不应该能活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Logically, you should all be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我解答了你的疑惑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If I tell you how we survived,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你会试着了解我们对这里的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}will you try to understand how we feel about our life here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,以及对彼此的感受吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}About each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:13:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知感情为何物，我是个科学家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Emotions are alien to me, I'm a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.41,0:13:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你也许骗得过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Someone else might believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你的船员，舰长，或是其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your shipmates, your captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但你骗不了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.50,0:13:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,桑多瓦尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Sandoval, within the hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚收到来自星舰指挥部的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've received orders from Starfleet Command
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,需要撤离殖民地所有居民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to evacuate all personnel from this colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以，你应该通知他们开始准备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Naturally, you'll inform your people to begin preparations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会在进取号上为你们提供食宿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We will have accommodations for you aboard the Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我拒绝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,先生，这并不是我自己的主意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not an arbitrary decision on my part, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我需要执行的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，这条命令完全是多余的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, it's entirely unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这里很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're in no danger here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:14:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经向你解释过博托射线的危害了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've explained the Berthold rays to you and their effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你还不清楚吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，我怎么才能让你明白呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor, how can l make you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.73,0:14:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你的仪器已经显示，我们全员都非常健康\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your own instruments have shown that we're all in perfect health.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人因为射线而死去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've had no deaths here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那你们的牲畜呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What about your animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是素食者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're vegetarians.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没有回答我的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That doesn't answer my question, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你们的牲畜都死了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why did all your animals die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，请不要在意这些细枝末节\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, you stress very unimportant matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是不会离开的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We will not leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,快到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's not much further.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没告诉我这是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've not yet explained the nature of this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那并不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Its basic properties and elements are not important.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的是它给我们带来了生命，和平，还有爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is important is, it gives life, peace, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你所说的…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What you're describing...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:15:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,…该不会是镇静剂吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...was once known in the vernacular as a happiness pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个科学家，应该明白那不能用来抵抗射线\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you, as a scientist, should know that that's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我是首批发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was one of the first to find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这些孢子的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The spores.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,孢子？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spores?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你不应该觉得难受的啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It shouldn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.28,0:15:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不应该是这样的，我们都没感受到痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not like this. It didn't hurt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你们不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经成为了我们的一员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now you belong to all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.19,0:16:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都是一样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And we to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用再藏着自己了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no need to hide your inner face any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们心意相通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.42,0:16:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，补充记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, supplemental.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们受星舰指挥部之令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have been ordered by starfleet Command
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,来到ο3号行星撤离当地殖民者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to evacuate the colony on Omicron III.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是殖民地领袖伊莱亚斯·桑多瓦尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}However, the colony leader, Elias sandoval,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,拒绝合作，并且不听取任何意见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}has refused all cooperation and will not listen to any arguments.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 桑多瓦尔 - 舰长，你的要求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Sandoval. - Captain, your arguments
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,非常正当，但我们不会接受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are very valid, but they do not apply to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是在无理取闹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're being unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思，失陪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, nevertheless. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我的任务是撤离所有的殖民地居民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My orders are to remove all the colonists,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,无论你合作与否，我都会完成任务\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and that's exactly what I intend to do, with or without your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕你要靠自己了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Without, I should think.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,要用武力制服他吗，吉姆？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Would you like to use a butterfly net on him, Jim?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不，我不希望… - 舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- No, I don't think I'll use a-- - Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们检查了所有东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've checked out everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,除了没见到动物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It all seems normal
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,一切似乎都正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}except for the absence of any animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要把居民撤离至第27星际基地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have orders to evacuate all colonists to Starbase 27.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,登陆部队必须协助他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I want landing parties to coordinate the colonists
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,准备把他们传送到星舰上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and prepare them to transport up to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要准备额外的食宿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll need extra accommodations aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克和德赛尔呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where's Mr. Spock and Mr. DeSalle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,检查工作开始之后我们就没看到过他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We haven't seen them since we began our check.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,德赛尔说他要去看看一些本地植物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}DeSalle said he was going to examine some native plants he found.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克有呼叫过吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did Spock call in at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克请回复…苏鲁，去看看登陆部队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock. See to the landing parties, will you, Mr. Sulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那块云看起像就像一条龙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That one looks like a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到尾巴和背脊了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see the tail and the dorsal spines?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没见过龙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've never seen a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.78,0:18:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我见过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在贝伦加丽亚7号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On Berengaria VII.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前没留意过云朵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I've never stopped to look at clouds before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还有彩虹\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or rainbows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我很清楚彩虹形成的原理\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you know I can tell you exactly why one appears in the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.26,0:18:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但我还没欣赏过它的美丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but considering its beauty has always been out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里，你会改变的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.83,0:19:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，你想怎样？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, what did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，是你吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，舰长，你到底想干嘛？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, captain. What did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't believe I want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克，我不知道你怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock, I don't know what you think you're doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but this is an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,10分钟内回到定居点向我报到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Report back to me at the settlement in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要把所有的居民撤到第27号星际基地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're evacuating all colonists to Starbase 27.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.31,0:19:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我拒绝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.32,0:19:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你拒绝什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't think so, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.15,0:19:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我拒绝，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't think so, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧向我报到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Report to me immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,快回复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Acknowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,通讯没有中断，但他不回复了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The frequency is open, but he doesn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那听起来一点也不像是史波克，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That didn't sound at all like Spock, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是说希望他能圆滑一点吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought you said you might like him if he mellowed a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我可没那么说过 - 你说过的，我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I didn't say that. - You said that. I--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他可能有麻烦了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He might be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，你负责接管登陆部队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, take over the landing party detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,把居民送上星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Start getting those colonists aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么找史波克？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How will you find Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他的通讯装置还开着，可以被定位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The frequency is open. It'll act as a homing device.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,联系德赛尔，让他来这和你会合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Contact DeSalle. Have him meet you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,把登陆部队分成二人小组\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Make sure the landing party works in teams of two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望有任何人落单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't want anybody left alone down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克先生？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么，德赛尔？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you doing with those things, DeSalle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你能看看这些东西，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Want you to take a good close look at these, doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.15,0:21:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能会感兴趣的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.44,0:21:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你疯了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you out of your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.45,0:21:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该立即汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were told to report to me at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.16,0:21:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想汇报，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't want to, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，看得出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,卡罗米小姐，希望你能跟我们回定居点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Miss Kalomi, you'll have to come back with us to the settlement
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,准备前往星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and prepare to transport up to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.55,0:22:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要撤离了，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There'll be no evacuation, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.64,0:22:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们该回去让你清醒清醒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But perhaps we should go back and get you straightened out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,苏鲁，抓住史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Sulu, Mr. Spock is under arrest,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,看好他，直到我们回到进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and he's in your custody until we get back to the Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.99,0:22:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.61,0:22:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.80,0:22:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,苏鲁先生，现在明白了吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Sulu understands, don't you, Mr. Sulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.56,0:23:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes. I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不应该对居民进行撤离\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course we can't remove the colony. It'd be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道这是什么植物，也不知道它做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know what these plants are or how they work on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.40,0:23:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但我命令你们跟我回村里去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but you're all going back to the settlement with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.66,0:23:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,而且，撤离任务如期执行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and those colonists are going aboard the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,看来舰长要变得孤立无援了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can see the captain is going to be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.26,0:23:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,准备传送\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready to beam up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.30,0:23:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，小吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hiya, Jimmy boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.26,0:23:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，我已经处理好所有事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, I've taken care of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你尽管放心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, all y'all gotta do is just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.14,0:23:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是医嘱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Doctor's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.06,0:23:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你送上去多少人了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How many of those did you beam up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.77,0:23:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大概100人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Must be might nigh on to 1 00 by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,医生，传送装置准备就绪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, doc, I'm ready to energize.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.94,0:23:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那些植物还好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything okay with those plants?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.78,0:23:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我是舰长，把我传送上去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the captain. Beam me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.49,0:23:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, sure. If you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.70,0:24:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I most certainly do. Energize.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.63,0:24:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.50,0:24:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,给我联系星际舰队的寇马克上将\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Put me through to Admiral Komack at Starfleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, I'm sorry, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我做不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.80,0:24:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么意思？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you mean, you can't do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.35,0:24:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,按标准程序通讯，这是命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Follow standard procedure, that's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.31,0:24:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know it is, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.48,0:24:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但所有通讯都中断了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you see, all communications are out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.61,0:24:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,中断了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Out?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.77,0:24:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它们都切断了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I short-circuited them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.03,0:24:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,除了和殖民地的通讯，我们还用得着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Except for ship-to-surface, we'll need that for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.16,0:24:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为了大家好，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's really for the best, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.18,0:25:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,回到各自岗位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go back to your stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.64,0:25:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,回到各自岗位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get back to your stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.85,0:25:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，长官，我们要加入那些殖民者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry, sir. We're all transporting down to join the colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.56,0:25:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我命令你们回到各自岗位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I said, get back to your station.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.77,0:25:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不，长官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.11,0:25:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这是在造反\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is mutiny, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.66,0:25:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,没错，是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.27,0:25:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历3417.5\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 3417.5.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.31,0:25:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那种植物孢子经过通风系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The pod plants have spread spores throughout the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.90,0:25:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,播散到了整个星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}carried by the ventilation system.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.78,0:25:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在它们的作用之下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Under their influence,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.78,0:25:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我的部下们热切地希望加入ο星殖民地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}my crew is deserting to join the Omicron colony,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.87,0:25:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,而我却无能为力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I can't stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.95,0:25:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不知为何我没受影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know why I have not been infected,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.83,0:25:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我也没办法让麦考伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}nor can I get Dr. McCoy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.42,0:25:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,向我解释这些孢子对人的身心影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to explain the physical-psychological aspects of the infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.17,0:25:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，我没兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not interested
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.63,0:26:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,解释这些东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}in any physical-psychological aspects, Jim boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.34,0:26:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这里都很健康\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We all perfectly healthy down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.85,0:26:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经听腻了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've heard that word a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.35,0:26:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,“完美”这个词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}"Perfect." Everything's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.93,0:26:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，但事实就是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, that's right. That's just what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.19,0:26:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你连扁桃体都长出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll bet you've even grown your tonsils back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.61,0:26:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sure enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.19,0:26:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，小吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hey, Jim boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.36,0:26:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你尝过乔治亚式的冰镇薄荷酒吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Y'all ever have a real cold, Georgia-style mint julep, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.03,0:26:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,听着，老骨头，我需要你的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, Bones, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.20,0:26:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你能进行什么测试，来帮我们研究\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you run tests, blood samples, anything at all to give us a lead
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.37,0:26:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这些植物的性质，找到摆脱影响的方法吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on what these things are, how to counteract them?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.67,0:26:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不想离开天堂呢，小吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who wants to counteract paradise, Jim boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.88,0:26:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊呼叫完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}McCoy out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.05,0:26:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,老骨头，老骨头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bones. Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.10,0:26:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,现在几乎所有舰队成员都下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Almost the entire ship's complement has beamed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.85,0:26:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm very pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.35,0:26:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,登陆计划现在进行得非常顺利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The entire landing operation is proceeding quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.61,0:27:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,麦考伊在哪？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where's McCoy?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.69,0:27:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他去调制薄荷酒了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He went off to create something called a mint julep.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.07,0:27:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是一种饮料，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's a drink, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.41,0:27:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，为什么你不加入我们呢？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, why don't you join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.16,0:27:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,加入你们所谓的天堂？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In your own private paradise?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.16,0:27:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是那些孢子的功劳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The spores have made it that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.12,0:27:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,它们来自哪里？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where did they originate?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.83,0:27:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这个很难说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's impossible to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.92,0:27:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,它们在太空中漂流，直至在这里生根发芽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They drifted through space until they finally landed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.42,0:27:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,它们能在博托射线照射下茁壮成长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You see, they actually thrive on Berthold rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.59,0:27:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,数以千计的微小孢子藏身于那种植物体内\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The plants act as a repository for thousands of microscopic spores
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.31,0:27:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,直到它们找到人类宿主\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}until they find a human body to inhabit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.06,0:27:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,作为回报，它们给人带来健康和安宁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In return, they give you complete health and peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.15,0:27:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,让人仿佛置身于天堂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.02,0:27:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们无欲无求，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have no need or want, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.28,0:27:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是真正的伊甸园，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a true Eden, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.78,0:27:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有爱和归属\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's belonging and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.62,0:27:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,无欲无求？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No wants, no needs?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.91,0:27:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可我们并不应该这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We weren't meant for that. None of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.33,0:27:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没有需求，没有欲望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Man stagnates if he has no ambition,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.63,0:28:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,人类的发展就会停滞不前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}no desire to be more than he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.88,0:28:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有我们需要的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have what we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.05,0:28:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但你们的生活没有挑战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Except a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.47,0:28:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你不明白，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't understand, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.09,0:28:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但你迟早会回来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But you'll come around, sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.22,0:28:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,加入我们吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.52,0:28:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.06,0:28:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回星舰了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm going back to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.24,0:29:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,轮机室，斯科特？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Engineering. Scotty?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.49,0:29:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,生化实验室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Biochemistry lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.12,0:29:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,安保\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Security.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.79,0:29:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还有人在舰上吗，我是舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is there anyone onboard? This is the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.23,0:29:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，星历3417.7\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, stardate 3417.7.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.37,0:29:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,除了我以外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Except for myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.95,0:30:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,全体船员都登陆到了星球上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}all crew personnel have transported to the surface of the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.75,0:30:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,一场哗变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mutinied.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.25,0:30:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,乌苏拉上尉完全破坏了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Uhura has effectively sabotaged
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.63,0:30:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,通讯装置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the communications station.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.72,0:30:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能与星球取得联系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can only contact the surface of the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.14,0:30:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,星舰可以在轨道上运行数月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The ship can be maintained in orbit for several months.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.93,0:30:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但即使有自动操控系统，我也无法独自驾驶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But even with automatic controls, I cannot pilot her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.31,0:30:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经被困在了这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In effect, I am marooned here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.88,0:30:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我开始意识到…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm beginning to realise...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.30,0:30:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,…这艘星舰是如此宏伟，如此的安静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...just how big this ship really is, how quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.72,0:30:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道怎样才能让我的船员回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know how to get my crew back,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.47,0:31:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样才能对抗那些孢子的作用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}how to counteract the effect of the spores.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.73,0:31:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道如何对抗…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know what I can offer against...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.44,0:31:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,…天堂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.69,0:31:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号呼叫史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise to Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.48,0:31:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，怎么了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, Jim, what is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.73,0:31:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我加入你们了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've joined you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.11,0:31:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.20,0:31:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wonderful, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.91,0:31:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么时候下来？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When will you beam down?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.74,0:32:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有一些东西要收拾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are some things in my quarters I want to pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.08,0:32:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.41,0:32:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我和利拉会在传送点等你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Leila and I will meet you at the beam-down point.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.33,0:32:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,寇克呼叫完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kirk out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.99,0:33:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.42,0:33:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.25,0:33:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,…不能…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.13,0:33:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,…走！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.22,0:33:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,情绪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.35,0:33:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,强烈的情绪，欲望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Violent emotions. Needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.19,0:33:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,愤怒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.92,0:34:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长日志，补充记录\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's log, supplemental.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.25,0:34:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我似乎找到了答案\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think I've discovered the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.51,0:34:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但要实现我的计划，需要冒一点风险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But to carry out my plan entails considerable risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.18,0:34:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克比一般的人更强大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock is much stronger than the ordinary human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.51,0:34:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,要是激怒了他，他可以轻而易举地掐死我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aroused, his great physical strength could kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.27,0:34:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但我必须冒这个险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it's a risk I'll have to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.23,0:34:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,进取号呼叫史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise to Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.07,0:34:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我是史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Spock here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.53,0:34:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我是吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.99,0:34:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么还没下来，吉姆？我们在等你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's keeping you, Jim? We've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.74,0:34:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我在收拾东西的时候发现了一些装备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been packing some things, and I realised there's some equipment here
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.24,0:34:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,也许能在下面派上用场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that we should have down at the settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.87,0:34:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,如果现在不拿下去，就没机会再回来拿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, we can't come back onboard once the last of us has left.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.75,0:34:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我要派一支小队帮你吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you want me to beam up a party?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.46,0:35:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我想你我两人就够了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I think you and I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.96,0:35:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在能上来吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why don't you beam up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.43,0:35:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.39,0:35:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我很快就回来，好吗？ - 我等你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It won't take long. Do you mind? - I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.40,0:35:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我准备好了，吉姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready to beam up, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.57,0:35:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,启动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Energizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.74,0:35:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个叛徒，不忠的、程序化的杂种\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, you mutinous, disloyal, computerised half-breed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.46,0:35:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,居然让我的舰队变成了这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll see about you deserting my ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.96,0:35:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我是“杂种”，我可以理解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The term "half-breed" is somewhat applicable.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.76,0:35:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但“程序化”说得并不准确\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But "computerised" is inaccurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.43,0:35:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,机器可以是程序化的，但人不可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A machine can be computerised, not a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.22,0:35:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为你是人？你只是一只体型过大的长耳野兔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What makes you think you're a man? You're an overgrown jackrabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.02,0:35:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,甲状腺亢奋的怪物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An elf with a hyperactive thyroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.77,0:35:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 吉姆，我不明白 - 你当然不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Jim, I don't understand. - Of course you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.48,0:36:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本没有脑子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't have the brains to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.23,0:36:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你的脑袋里装的只是一些电路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All you have is printed circuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.61,0:36:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 舰长，我想我要失陪了 - 你觉得一个由机器和百科全书所生的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Captain, if you'll excuse me-- - What can you expect
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.07,0:36:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,只会傻笑，耳朵长得像怪物的杂种\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from a simpering, devil-eared freak whose father was a computer
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.03,0:36:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,脑子里能有些什么东西？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and his mother an encyclopaedia?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.66,0:36:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我的母亲是一名教师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My mother was a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.95,0:36:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,而我的父亲，是一名大使\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My father, an ambassador.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.96,0:36:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你的父亲是一台机器，就和你一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your father was a computer, like his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.13,0:36:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一个来自充满叛徒的星球的大使\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}An ambassador from a planet of traitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.30,0:36:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦肯人完全没有诚信可言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A Vulcan never lived who had an ounce of integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.76,0:36:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，请不要再…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, please don't--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.47,0:36:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你和你的族人一样，都是叛徒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're a traitor from a race of traitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.51,0:36:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,对上级不忠，你和你的低等种族都会下地狱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Disloyal to the core. Rotten like the rest of your subhuman race.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.10,0:36:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有胆子去和那个女的鬼混\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And you've got the gall to make love to that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.90,0:36:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,够了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.73,0:36:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,她知道你是什么东西吗，史波克？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Does she know what she's getting, Spock?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.82,0:36:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,一个会说话的，等着发霉的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A carcass full of memory banks
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.91,0:36:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,行尸走肉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who should be squatting on a mushroom
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.37,0:36:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是一个活人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}instead of passing himself off as a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.24,0:36:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该去马戏团跟小丑待在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You belong in a circus, Spock, not a starship.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.67,0:37:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right next to the dog-faced boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.50,0:37:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样了？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.54,0:37:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我没想到你生气了会是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't realise what it took to get under that thick hide of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.30,0:37:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不过无论如何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Anyhow, I don't know what you're so mad about.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.97,0:37:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不是每个大副都有机会这样狠揍舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It isn't every first officer who gets to belt his captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.18,0:37:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好几次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.23,0:37:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你是故意侮辱我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You did that to me deliberately.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.19,0:37:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Believe me, Mr. Spock,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.69,0:37:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,受伤的不只是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it was painful in more ways than one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.99,0:38:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那些孢子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The spores.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.99,0:38:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,作用消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.28,0:38:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我清醒过来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't belong anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.12,0:38:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你说它们给你带来了安宁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You said they were benevolent and peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.12,0:38:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,激烈的情绪能对抗并且消灭它们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Violent emotions overwhelm them, destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.87,0:38:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须激怒你以摆脱它们的影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had to make you angry enough to shake off their influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.54,0:38:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是答案，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's the answer, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.88,0:38:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你也许是对的，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That may be correct, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.76,0:38:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但要通过这种方式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But trying to initiate a brawl
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.51,0:38:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,让超过500名船员恢复理智是不切实际的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with over 500 crew men and colonists is hardly logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.01,0:38:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一个办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had something else in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.72,0:38:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你能制造一个次声发射机吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can you put together a subsonic transmitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.60,0:38:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以用它来入侵通讯站\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Something we could hook into the communications station
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.23,0:38:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,把信息广播出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and broadcast over the communicator?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.69,0:38:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可以 - 好的，我们开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It can be done. - Good. Let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.45,0:38:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.12,0:38:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,攻击舰队官员是一项重罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Striking a fellow officer is a court-martial offence.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.92,0:38:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我们都进了禁闭室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, if we're both in the brig,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.71,0:38:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来制造发射机？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who's gonna build the subsonic transmitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.38,0:39:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的的确符合逻辑，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That is quite logical, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.23,0:39:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,利拉小姐，现在就开始数星星好像有点早了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, now, it's a little early to be counting stars, Miss Leila.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.06,0:39:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我在等史波克和舰长下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm waiting for Mr. Spock and the captain to transport down.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.44,0:39:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还要拿一些装备\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They have some equipment to be moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.28,0:39:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们已经在上面待了很久了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.86,0:39:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望他们能早点下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wish he'd come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.45,0:39:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来帮帮你吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, now, I think I can fix that for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.16,0:39:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.04,0:39:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是进取号，我是史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise. Spock here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.14,0:39:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我是利拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Leila.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.26,0:39:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我借了医生的通讯器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I borrowed the doctor's communicator.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.47,0:39:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我还在担心你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was worried something might have happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.35,0:39:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You are all right, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.15,0:40:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.40,0:40:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我…我很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, I'm-- I'm quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.49,0:40:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我能上去吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can I come aboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.32,0:40:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没参观过星舰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've never seen a starship before.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.33,0:40:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我想见你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.83,0:40:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你还在传送点吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you still at the beam-down point?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.21,0:40:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,医疗官在那吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And is the doctor there?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.08,0:40:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我们都在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, to both questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.38,0:40:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的通讯器给麦考伊医生吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Give your communicator back to Dr. McCoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.67,0:40:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用带着那个上来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You won't need it to beam up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.01,0:40:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可能要花一点时间，你等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It'll take a few moments. Just wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.51,0:40:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫完毕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.39,0:40:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.85,0:40:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我不该干涉你和卡罗米小姐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Miss Kalomi is strictly your concern, but should you talk to her
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.03,0:40:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但她现在还带着孢子，你不该和她讲话吧？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}while she's still under the influence of the spores?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.37,0:40:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我很快就回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll be back shortly, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.12,0:41:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经不属于我们了，是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're no longer with us, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.21,0:41:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我感到了异常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I felt something was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.75,0:41:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.71,0:41:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我回去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come back to the planet with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.80,0:41:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以重新成为我们的一员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can belong again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.26,0:41:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我回去吧，求你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come back with me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.26,0:41:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.53,0:42:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.57,0:42:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我六年前就说过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I said that six years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.95,0:42:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我的心从来就没变过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I can't seem to stop repeating myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.41,0:42:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,在地球上的时候，你没做任何表示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On Earth, you couldn't give anything of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.33,0:42:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,连拥抱都没有过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You couldn't even put your arms around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.13,0:42:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的爱情没法在那里开花结果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We couldn't have anything together there.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.67,0:42:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在别的地方也是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We couldn't have anything together anyplace else.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.47,0:42:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但在这里，我们都会快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But we're happy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.26,0:42:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能失去你，史波克，我不能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't lose you now, Mr. Spock. I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.56,0:42:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须对这艘星舰负责\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have a responsibility to this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.53,0:42:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,对舰桥上的那个男人负责\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To that man on the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.78,0:42:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是我，利拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am what I am, Leila,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.66,0:43:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如果每个人都不得不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and if there are self-made purgatories,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.66,0:43:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,生活在自己造就的炼狱中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we all have to live in them,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.88,0:43:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我的人生并不是最糟糕的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}mine can be no worse than someone else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.92,0:43:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经失去你了，是吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have lost you, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.85,0:43:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不止是你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not only you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.35,0:43:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,还有它们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've lost all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.10,0:43:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那些孢子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The spores.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.02,0:43:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,它们的作用消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've lost them too.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.77,0:43:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长发现，强烈的情绪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The captain discovered that strong emotions
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.57,0:43:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,还有欲望可以抵抗那些孢子的影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and needs destroy the spore influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.87,0:43:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是为了我好吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And this is for my good?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.41,0:43:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我能继续爱你吗？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you mind if I say I still love you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.72,0:44:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没告诉过我你的另一个名字，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You never told me if you had another name, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.57,0:44:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你念不出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You couldn't pronounce it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.66,0:44:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不会直接听到这些信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They'll not hear this, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.25,0:44:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们会感受得到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It'll be more of a sensation of feeling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.75,0:44:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就像有人把痒粉洒在他们身上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As though somebody had put itching powder on their skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.71,0:44:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.38,0:44:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,几分钟之后就会起效了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, it should begin to work on their nerves in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.77,0:44:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 抱歉，德赛尔 - 你这是在干什么？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Sorry, DeSalle. - What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.27,0:44:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我说了，对不起 - 真是笨手笨脚的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I said I was sorry. - More like you're clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.78,0:44:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你没挡着我的道…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you hadn't gotten in my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.63,0:45:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,别打了，别打了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come on, break it up. Break it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.69,0:45:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.31,0:45:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在想应该给你安排什么工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I've been thinking about what sort of work I can assign you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.36,0:45:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是什么意思？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.82,0:45:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什么工作？我是医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What sort of work? I'm a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.65,0:45:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不再是了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not anymore, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.99,0:45:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不需要医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We don't need you. Not as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.16,0:45:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.41,0:45:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你信不信我现在就把你打到进医院？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Would you like to see just how fast I can put you in a hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.67,0:45:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我是这个殖民地的首领\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am the leader of this colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.50,0:45:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我会给你安排任何我觉得合适的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll assign you to whatever work I think is suitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.30,0:46:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.55,0:46:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,最好让我当个技工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Better make me a mechanic.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.59,0:46:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我就可以修理你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then I can treat little tin gods like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.07,0:46:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起，桑多瓦尔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sorry, Sandoval.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.24,0:46:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道我是怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know what made me do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.00,0:46:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这里什么都没干\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've done nothing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.37,0:46:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没有成就，没有进展\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No accomplishments. No progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.17,0:46:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,浪费了三年时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Three years wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.38,0:46:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们希望把这个星球改造成花园\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We wanted to make this planet a garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.14,0:46:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能留在这里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.27,0:46:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没有了那些孢子，你活不下去的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can't survive without the spores.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.40,0:47:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,到达星际基地之后，你可以重新开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}After you've cleared at the starbase, you could be relocated.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.11,0:47:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,去你想去的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It depends upon what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.86,0:47:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.24,0:47:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我会继续工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think we'd like to get some work done.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.08,0:47:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,完成以前的理想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The work we started out to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.29,0:47:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,呼叫进取号\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.17,0:47:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是进取号，我是史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enterprise. Spock here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.84,0:47:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我是麦考伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is McCoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.76,0:47:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,桑多瓦尔想和舰长谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sandoval would like to talk to the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.88,0:47:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.72,0:47:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们开始跟我们联系了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're all beginning to call in, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.56,0:47:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好像有点懊恼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Rather contritely, I should say.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.56,0:47:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,桑多瓦尔希望和你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sandoval wishes to speak to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.27,0:47:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,打开扬声器，我是寇克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Put him on the speaker. Kirk here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.77,0:47:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,舰长，我之前听说你要把我们送到27号星际基地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, as I understood it, you were to transport us to Starbase 27.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.73,0:47:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会配合你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll give you every cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.28,0:47:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,开始准备吧，桑多瓦尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Start making preparations, Mr. Sandoval.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.91,0:47:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们的船员都上来后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll begin transporting your people aboard
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.29,0:47:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就开始传送你们的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as soon as more of our crew checks in.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.72,0:48:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆，我刚检查完最后一个居民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, Jim, I've just examined the last of the colonists.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.14,0:48:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都很健康\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're all in absolutely perfect, perfect health.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.98,0:48:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这是那些孢子带来的小福利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A fringe benefit left over by the spores.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.19,0:48:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.11,0:48:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这是人们第二次被赶出天堂了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, that's the second time man's been thrown out of paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.03,0:48:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不，老骨头，这次是我们自己走出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, no, Bones. This time we walked out on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.66,0:48:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,也许天堂并不适合我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe we weren't meant for paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.16,0:48:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们就应该不断奋斗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe we were meant to fight our way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.63,0:48:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,挣扎，努力，一步一步地走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Struggle, claw our way up, scratch for every inch of the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.63,0:48:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也许无法控制生活的节奏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe we can't stroll to the music of the lute.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.09,0:48:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们必须紧跟这种节奏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We must march to the sound of drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.51,0:48:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这是在吟诗吗，舰长？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Poetry, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.10,0:48:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不像是你啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Non-regulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.31,0:48:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你对这次行动有什么感想呢，史波克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We haven't heard much from you about Omicron Ceti III, Mr. Spock.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.10,0:49:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有什么想说的，舰长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have little to say about it, captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.69,0:49:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不过…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Except that...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.32,0:49:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,…一生之中我第一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...for the first time in my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.49,0:49:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,觉得快乐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was happy.
